Towards a second generation of ‘social media metrics’: Characterizing Twitter communities of attention around science

    Adrián A. Díaz-Faes ,

    Roles Conceptualization, Data curation, Formal analysis, Investigation, Methodology, Visualization, Writing – original draft, Writing – review & editing

    * E-mail: diazfaes@ingenio.upv.es

    Affiliation INGENIO (CSIC-UPV), Universitat Politécnica de València, Valencia, Spain

    ORCID logo http://orcid.org/0000-0003-1928-4608
    ⨯
    Timothy D. Bowman,

    Roles Conceptualization, Data curation, Investigation, Writing – review & editing

    Affiliation School of Information Sciences, Wayne State University, Detroit, Michigan, United States of America
    ⨯
    Rodrigo Costas

