Towards a second generation of ‘social media metrics’: Characterizing Twitter communities of attention around science

    Adrián A. Díaz-Faes, 
    Timothy D. Bowman, 
    Rodrigo Costas

PLOS
x

    Published: May 22, 2019
    https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0216408

    Article
    Authors
    Metrics
    Comments
    Media Coverage

